Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:45.66,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wanna kiss you, love me baby
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:04.59,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ねえ、私朝から思考回路が大渋滞です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:10.39,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}前みたいに気の抜けた顔なんてしないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:15.81,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}偶然を装うための計算をして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:22.48,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君に掛ける言葉　必死に探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:27.87,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}上手に話せる自信なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:33.37,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}これっぽっちもないくせにね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.25,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君にkiss you, love me baby
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.17,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}始まったばかりのストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.63,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}予習も何もできてないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:39.82,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wanna kiss you, love me baby
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:45.66,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wanna kiss you, love me baby
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:04.59,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一大早的我  思维就已经水泄不通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:10.39,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}再也装不出无精打采的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:15.81,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不仅要算好偶遇上你的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:22.48,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}还要为了向你说的话思前想后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:27.87,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只是哪怕一句心里话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:33.37,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}都没有信心向你倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.25,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}送你kiss you, love me baby
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.17,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我的故事刚刚翻开第一篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.63,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}哪怕没有丝毫的预习和准备
